### Instructions

1. Create two files, `index.html` and `styles.css`.
2. Copy the HTML code into the `index.html` file.
3. Copy the CSS code into the `styles.css` file.
4. Replace placeholder text and images with your actual content and images.
5. Open the `index.html` file in a web browser to see your portfolio website.

Feel free to customize the styles and content to better fit your personal brand!
